###################################################################################
# Guidelines & Tips for first-time users
###################################################################################

1. In the document that follows, when you read "[version]" substitute with current info.
  For example - if the downloaded package version is 1.0.0 change enmasse-distro-[version] to enmasse-distro-1.0.0

2. The source code for this project is located under enmasse-distro-[version]/src folder.

3. For EnMasse Services-level documentation, jump to SECTION 5.
