###################################################################################
# SECTION 3:  Instructions to setup EnMasse development environment
###################################################################################

1. Install Fortress to local Maven repository.
Note: for this evaluation simply copy the contents of 'fortress' folder located in package to your configured maven2 repository on the target machine.
For example: /home/user/.m2/repository

2. open a command prompt on target machine in the root folder of the EnMasse source package, ./enmasse-distro-[version]/

3. set java home:
>export JAVA_HOME=/opt/jdk1.6.0_27/

4. set maven home:
>export M2_HOME=/usr/share/maven2

5. run maven install:
>mvn install
